page.title: 11NATURE AND WILDLIFE
page.content:
Seashore and marsh along Prinsted harbour(shingle foreshore).Fields and gardens behind. BIRDS SEEN DESCRIPTION
Black headed gull,grey wings and back blackhead and tail,orange beak and legs. Feral pigeon,short beak,orange legs. Collard Dove,brown back,white and black wings. House Martins,black & white back forked tail. Pied Wagtail,grey back,black head & bib. Robin,brown back and red breast. Blackbird,black or dull brown,yellow beak. Chaffinch,slightly forked tail,pink breast. Linnet,brown back,pink or cream breast. (CONT.)
